name: Icel Idman Yurdu
description: What is Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Token (MIY)? Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Token is the official fan token of the Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Football Club, a sports club taking place in the Turkish League. MIY is the fan token that is used for: Enabling fans to engage and communicate with the Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Football Club Receiving gifts, accessing privileges, discounts, special events. How Many MIY Tokens Are There in Circulation? Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Token launched on April 13, 2022 with 1.1 Million MIY tokens created at genesis. %90 of the tokens sold out at pre-sale on Bitexen. Currently, 1,079,068.00 MIY token are in circulation. Who Are the Founders of MIY Token ? Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Token ($MIY) project is launched in cooperation with ExenPay, Bitexen and Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Football Club. Where Can I Buy Icel Idman Yurdu Spor Token (MIY)? MIY is available for trading on Bitexen, one of the largest exchanges in Turkey, available.
